	<p>The enactment of the federal Telecommunications Act of 1996 and the whirlwind pace of technological advancement means the telecommunications industry requires up-to-date strategic advice on myriad federal and state regulatory issues.</p>
<h2>Premier Telecommunications Law Firm</h2>
<p>We have established our Firm as the premier telecommunications law Firm in Nebraska, routinely representing clients before the Federal Communications Commission and Nebraska Public Service Commission. </p>
<p>Our attorneys routinely appear before the Nebraska PSC and are in constant contact with members of the Nebraska PSC and their staff. When it comes to legal and regulatory changes in Nebraska, we have the resources to help our clients keep a step ahead of the competition.</p>
<h2>Interdisciplinary Approach</h2>
<p>The breadth of practice area experience in our Firm allows us to take an interdisciplinary approach to our clients' needs. Our attorneys routinely advise clients on taxation, entities choice and governance, commercial transactions, employment and labor matters, and securities and finance issues.</p>
